ESTá FUMANDO LA MOTA, HMM?

12:39.084 --> 12:41.856
AH. TAL VEZ
ESTá COGIENDO EL MR. DOUG.

12:41.890 --> 12:44.094
[ LAUGHS ]
AY, POR FAVOR.

12:44.127 --> 12:44.996
QUé FEO.

12:45.029 --> 12:47.133
AY, NADIE CHINGA
SEÑOR DOUG.

12:47.167 --> 12:48.269
POBRECITO.

12:48.302 --> 12:49.606
POBRECITO.

12:49.639 --> 12:51.075
MIRA. CON TODA SINCERIDAD,

12:51.108 --> 12:53.446
YO CREO LO QUE
ALEJANDRO DICE.

12:53.479 --> 12:55.016
ALEJANDRO ES UN COMEMIERDA.

12:55.049 --> 12:56.418
AH, vSí?
ESTá LLENO DE MIERDA

12:56.452 --> 12:59.024
PORQUE LA SEÑORA TUYA
LE ESTá VENDIENDO LA MIERDA.

12:59.057 --> 13:00.126
AY.

13:06.372 --> 13:07.842
WHAT ARE YOU LOOKING FOR?

13:07.875 --> 13:09.812
ARE YOU STEALING FROM US?

13:09.846 --> 13:12.384
YES. MY FAMILY
NEED THIS MENORAH.

13:12.417 --> 13:15.156
MOM SAID YOU ONCE
STOLE ONE OF HER RINGS.

13:15.189 --> 13:15.958
WHAT?

13:15.991 --> 13:17.394
BUT THEN SHE FOUND IT.

13:20.466 --> 13:23.974
I THINK YOU JUST PROBABLY WANT
TO PUT YOUR SAFE RIGHT HERE.

13:24.007 --> 13:26.078
I'LL PAY YOU
TO INSTALL IT.

13:26.111 --> 13:27.648
YOU'RE ALREADY INTO ME
FOR A CAR HOOD,

13:27.682 --> 13:29.051
AND I AIN'T SEEN A DIME
OF THAT.

13:29.084 --> 13:30.486
YOU GOTTA OFFER ME
SOMETHING ELSE.

13:30.521 --> 13:31.690
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

13:31.723 --> 13:34.829
HELLO. NANCY?

13:34.862 --> 13:37.067
CELIA, WHAT
ARE YOU DOING HERE?

13:37.100 --> 13:40.073
I REFUSE TO JUST SIT
AROUND THE HOUSE

13:40.106 --> 13:42.077
FOR THREE DAYS, WAITING.

13:42.110 --> 13:43.547
[ SIGHS ]

13:43.580 --> 13:45.918
THE PUPPIES ARE COMING OFF,
NANCE.

13:45.951 --> 13:47.120
AND I'M THINKING,

13:47.153 --> 13:50.460
IT'S TIME TO TAKE THEM OUT
FOR ONE LAST WALK.

13:52.598 --> 13:54.736
ALL RIGHT,
WHO'S THE HOTTY?

13:54.769 --> 13:55.771
MY CARPENTER.

13:55.804 --> 13:58.009
CONRAD.
CONRAD, THIS IS CELIA.

13:58.042 --> 13:59.679
HEY.

13:59.712 --> 14:02.918
HELLO, CARPENTER.

14:02.952 --> 14:05.858
DO YOU WANT TO SEE
SOMETHING?

14:05.891 --> 14:08.095
CELIA, YOU HAVE TO STOP
FLASHING YOUR BOOBS.

14:08.129 --> 14:10.033
OH, SPEAK WHEN SPOKEN TO.

14:11.536 --> 14:13.507
"HERE TODAY,
GONE TOMORROW."

14:13.540 --> 14:14.341
IT'S SYMBOLIC.

14:14.374 --> 14:17.681
MY HOMAGE
TO TEMPORARY PERMANENCE.

14:17.715 --> 14:19.351
THEY'RE BEAUTIFUL.

14:19.384 --> 14:20.386
WHY, THANK YOU.

14:20.420 --> 14:23.159
WOULD YOU LIKE TO TAKE THEM OUT
DANCING TONIGHT?

14:23.192 --> 14:25.096
HE DOESN'T HAVE TIME
TO GO DANCING.

14:25.129 --> 14:27.835
COME ON. WE'LL GO OUT ‐‐
ALL OF US.

14:27.868 --> 14:31.108
I'VE BEEN FULLY WAXED,
AND I HAVE A BRAND‐NEW TATTOO.

14:31.141 --> 14:33.647
I AM NOT GONNA
TAKE "NO" FOR AN ANSWER.

14:33.680 --> 14:34.816
YOU HAVE A HUSBAND.

14:34.849 --> 14:36.786
MM‐HMM,
WHO'S WHITE AND JEWISH.

14:36.820 --> 14:39.959
IF WE WERE GOING OUT
FOR KREPLACH, MAYBE.

14:42.698 --> 14:43.867
HEY, HEY, HEY.

14:43.900 --> 14:46.271
NO MORE TYPING, ALL RIGHT?

14:46.305 --> 14:49.044
LET'S JUST TALK.

14:49.077 --> 14:50.647
I WANT TO HEAR YOUR VOICE.

14:51.783 --> 14:53.219
WHY NOT?

14:58.897 --> 15:01.034
HOW DO YOU KNOW?
YOU CAN'T HEAR IT.

15:01.068 --> 15:02.905
LISTEN, COME ON.

15:02.938 --> 15:05.944
I PROMISE YOU
IT'LL BE OKAY.

15:05.978 --> 15:09.017
JUST TALK ‐‐ IT'S ME, OKAY?
JUST TALK TO ME.

15:09.050 --> 15:13.058
PLEASE? PLEASE?
HEY!

15:13.092 --> 15:15.363
[ VIDEO GAME SOUND EFFECTS ]

15:18.235 --> 15:20.273
AAAAHH!

15:20.306 --> 15:22.878
TAKE THAT,
YOU KRAUT BASTARDS!

15:22.912 --> 15:24.347
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

15:24.381 --> 15:25.216
KILLING NAZIS.

15:25.249 --> 15:27.655
OH, HOW BRAVE.
DON'T HURT YOUR THUMBS.

15:29.257 --> 15:33.098
OH, SO NOW YOU'RE SELLING WEED
AND TURNING TRICKS.

15:33.132 --> 15:35.637
GIRL'S GOTTA SUPPORT TWO KIDS
AND A BROTHER‐IN‐LAW.

15:35.671 --> 15:38.610
NOT AFTER WE TURN THAT BAKERY
INTO A GOLD MINE.

15:38.643 --> 15:41.348
JUST LIKE THE JESUS T‐SHIRTS
AND THE OSTRICH FARM, HUH?

15:41.381 --> 15:44.087
YEAH, YOU'RE RIGHT.
MUCH BETTER TO BE A POT DEALER.

15:44.121 --> 15:47.227
I'M NOT GETTING SUCKED
INTO YOUR BULLSHIT RIGHT NOW.

15:47.260 --> 15:49.264
OKAY.
TAP INTO YOUR HIGHER POWER.

15:49.297 --> 15:51.636
IF I COULD TAP
INTO MY HIGHER POWER,

15:51.669 --> 15:53.472
MY FINGERS
WOULDN'T BE NUMB.

15:55.209 --> 15:57.147
MOM. MOM!
MOM, MOM, MOM.

15:57.180 --> 16:00.052
CHECK THIS OUT!
THIS IS SO COOL!

16:00.086 --> 16:01.121
ARE YOU GOING OUT?

16:01.155 --> 16:03.092
YEAH, SWEETIE,
BUT WE'LL LOOK AT THAT

16:03.125 --> 16:05.229
FIRST THING
IN THE MORNING, OKAY?

16:05.263 --> 16:06.398
BE GOOD.

16:07.802 --> 16:09.839
HEY, BUDDY, COME HANG
OUT WITH ME.

16:09.872 --> 16:11.175
PASS.

16:13.513 --> 16:16.986
[ DANCE MUSIC PLAYS ]

16:28.577 --> 16:30.046
IS IT TRUE WHAT THEY SAY

16:30.079 --> 16:32.985
THAT ONCE A WHITE WOMAN'S
BEEN WITH A CARPENTER,

16:33.018 --> 16:34.187
SHE NEVER GOES BACK?

16:34.221 --> 16:37.995
BABY, WHEN I NAIL SOMETHING,
IT STAYS NAILED.

16:38.028 --> 16:41.168
WAIT RIGHT HERE.

16:41.201 --> 16:44.107
I HAVE CANCER
AND JUNGLE FEVER,

16:44.140 --> 16:49.050
AND TONIGHT, ONE OF THEM
IS GOING TO GET CURED.

17:16.773 --> 17:18.375
[ SIGHS ]

17:19.912 --> 17:22.350
[ DANCE MUSIC PLAYS ]

17:56.051 --> 17:58.657
[ EXHALES SLOWLY ]

17:58.690 --> 17:59.992
HEY, SPONSOR.

18:00.026 --> 18:02.463
HI.

18:02.497 --> 18:04.167
UH...

18:04.200 --> 18:07.173
I'M REALLY LOSING IT.

18:07.206 --> 18:09.477
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU.

18:09.512 --> 18:11.148
UH...

18:11.181 --> 18:15.389
MY GIRLFRIEND
JUST BROKE UP WITH ME.

18:15.423 --> 18:17.260
NO, NO, NO.

18:17.293 --> 18:20.634
I NEED TO SEE YOU.

18:20.667 --> 18:22.671
<i>YOU'RE MOVE, CREEP.</i>

18:22.705 --> 18:25.109
I'M SITTING HERE WITH
A JOINT IN ONE HAND

18:25.142 --> 18:26.546
AND A LIGHTER IN THE OTHER.

18:26.579 --> 18:28.215
AND, UH...

18:28.248 --> 18:30.419
I'M NEVER GONNA MAKE IT
THROUGH THE NIGHT.

18:30.453 --> 18:33.760
PLEASE.
PLEASE, I'M BEGGING YOU.

18:38.503 --> 18:40.907
YOU GOT
A NICE BADUNKADUNK.

18:40.941 --> 18:43.145
HAS THIS EVER HAPPENED
TO YOU?

18:43.178 --> 18:45.249
YOU LIVE YOUR WHOLE LIFE
WITHOUT HEARING AN EXPRESSION,

18:45.282 --> 18:46.819
AND THEN YOU HEAR IT TWICE
IN ONE DAY.

18:46.853 --> 18:48.590
WOULD YOU LIKE
SOME CHAMPAGNE?

18:48.623 --> 18:49.692
NO, THANK YOU.

18:49.725 --> 18:51.996
SOMETHING TELLS ME IT'S BEST
TO STAY SOBER AROUND YOU.

18:52.030 --> 18:53.365
NOW, WHY WOULD YOU
SAY THAT?

18:53.399 --> 18:54.869
I HAD TO GO THROUGH
A METAL DETECTOR,

18:54.902 --> 18:57.240
BUT YOU AND YOUR FRIENDS CAME
THROUGH THE BACK ENTRANCE.

18:57.273 --> 18:58.743
THAT MAKES ME NERVOUS.

18:58.777 --> 18:59.779
I MAKE YOU NERVOUS?

18:59.812 --> 19:02.383
THE GUNS MAKE ME NERVOUS.
YOU MAKE ME CURIOUS.

19:02.417 --> 19:05.824
SAYS THE WHITE LADY
IN THE BLACK CLUB.

19:05.857 --> 19:08.563
WHAT'S YOUR STORY?

19:08.596 --> 19:09.598
I CAME WITH CONRAD.

19:09.632 --> 19:11.201
YOU BUYING OR SELLING?

19:12.638 --> 19:15.811
I'M THE SUBURBAN BARONESS
OF BUD.

19:15.844 --> 19:17.581
NANCY.

19:17.614 --> 19:18.650
TUSK.

19:18.683 --> 19:20.119
NICE TO MEET YOU, TUSK.

19:20.152 --> 19:21.188
WHAT DO YOU DO?

19:21.221 --> 19:22.624
I'M A BUSINESSMAN.

19:22.658 --> 19:24.294
ARE YOU NOW?

19:24.327 --> 19:25.864
DO YOU HAVE ANY KIDS?

19:27.835 --> 19:30.741
I DO ‐‐
TWO BOYS AND A GIRL.

19:30.774 --> 19:33.847
I HAVE TWO BOYS.
I'M NOT WITH THEM ENOUGH.

19:33.880 --> 19:36.986
HOW DO YOU KEEP YOUR BUSINESS
SEPARATE FROM YOUR FAMILY?

19:37.020 --> 19:38.255
THEY LIVE IN ATLANTA.

19:38.288 --> 19:40.092
DON'T YOU MISS THEM?

19:40.126 --> 19:42.363
I'D MISS THEM MORE
IF THEY WERE DEAD.

19:43.666 --> 19:45.036
YOU GOT A MAN?

19:45.069 --> 19:47.140
HE DIED OF A HEART ATTACK.

19:47.173 --> 19:49.812
HE WAS FUN.
WE HAD A GOOD FIT.

19:49.845 --> 19:50.947
NOW I RUN AROUND ALL DAY,

19:50.981 --> 19:52.651
AND I DON'T HAVE ANYONE
TO TALK TO.

19:52.684 --> 19:54.555
YOU'RE TALKING TO ME.

19:54.588 --> 19:55.557
WHAT AM I DOING?

19:55.590 --> 19:57.226
YOU'RE DOING WHAT ALL OF US
ARE DOING, BABY.

19:57.260 --> 19:58.630
YOU'RE GETTING BY.

20:05.443 --> 20:07.313
LUPITA!

20:07.346 --> 20:09.518
STILL LOOKING
FOR SOMETHING?

20:09.552 --> 20:12.256
I CLEANING.

20:12.290 --> 20:15.597
WELL, DO YOU WANT TO HELP ME
BUILD A PILLOW FORT?

20:15.630 --> 20:16.465
OKAY.

20:16.498 --> 20:19.404
THERE'S NOTHING
TO FIND HERE ANYWAY.

20:19.437 --> 20:21.876
I GET MORE PILLOWS.

20:29.023 --> 20:31.261
LUPITA, HURRY UP.

20:37.841 --> 20:39.612
[ GASPS ]

20:39.645 --> 20:41.114
[ SNIFFS ]

20:41.148 --> 20:43.452
DIOS MíO.

20:43.485 --> 20:47.226
ME AND MY GIRLFRIEND,
VANESSA ‐‐

20:47.260 --> 20:48.963
WE LOVED TO GET HIGH

20:48.997 --> 20:53.305
AND HAVE SPIRITUALLY
PASSIONATE, UNINHIBITED SEX.

20:53.338 --> 20:55.342
WASN'T EVEN SEX.
IT WAS BETTER THAN SEX.

20:55.376 --> 21:00.654
IT WAS LIKE A...
TANTRIC MIND MELD.

21:00.687 --> 21:03.192
ONLY WITH LESS MIND
AND MORE MELD.

21:03.225 --> 21:06.666
THAT'S WHY I HAVE TO GET
WASTED, YOU KNOW, BUT...

21:06.699 --> 21:08.368
[ SIGHS ]

21:08.402 --> 21:11.475
I KNOW THAT IT'S MAKING ME
MISS VALERIE EVEN MORE.

21:11.509 --> 21:16.619
AND THE PAIN WILL BE AS BAD
AS THE SEX WAS GOOD.

21:16.652 --> 21:17.521
I GET IT.

21:17.554 --> 21:19.190
NO, I DON'T THINK YOU DO.

21:19.224 --> 21:20.392
I REALLY LOVED VERONICA.

21:20.426 --> 21:22.263
NO, BELIEVE ME.
I GET IT.

21:22.296 --> 21:25.002
NOTHING USED TO MAKE ME
HAPPIER THAN...

21:25.035 --> 21:29.077
GETTING HIGH AND HAVING
PASSIONATE, UNINHIBITED SEX.

21:29.110 --> 21:30.212
REALLY?

21:30.246 --> 21:31.916
[ CHUCKLING ]

21:31.949 --> 21:34.788
YEAH, IN FACT, UM...

21:34.822 --> 21:36.391
WHAT?

21:36.424 --> 21:39.030
