22:19.812 --> 22:23.953
♪♪ KEEPING THE LITTLE GIRL
AS MY GOAL ♪♪

22:23.987 --> 22:28.362
♪♪ MAKES MY LIFE WORTH LIVING,
YOU KNOW ♪♪

22:28.395 --> 22:30.499
