23:03.533 --> 23:06.371
<i>YOU ARE SERIOUSLY</i>
<i>TWISTED‐STRANGE, BOTWIN.</i>

23:06.404 --> 23:08.743
<i>DON'T SAY MY NAME,</i>
<i>INFIDEL.</i>

23:11.983 --> 23:13.786
<i>HI, MOM!</i>

23:16.659 --> 23:19.163
