WITH HIM?

23:20.332 --> 23:22.905
HE SHOT A MOUNTAIN LION.
HE WROTE A GANGSTA RAP.

23:22.938 --> 23:24.575
NOW HE'S MAKING
TERRORIST VIDEOS.

23:24.608 --> 23:27.480
YEAH,
AND I MELTED ARMY MEN,

23:27.514 --> 23:30.185
AND I PEED
ON THE NEIGHBOR'S KID,

23:30.219 --> 23:31.789
AND I BLEW UP FROGS.

23:31.822 --> 23:32.624
I WAS YOUNG.

23:32.658 --> 23:35.195
IT WAS THE 4th OF JULY,
AND...

23:35.229 --> 23:37.366
JUDAH DARED ME.

23:37.400 --> 23:40.239
THE POINT IS IS THAT LITTLE
