SCORSESE ON OUR HANDS.

23:50.927 --> 23:53.733
CHICKS LOVE THOSE
CUTTING‐EDGE DIRECTORS.

23:53.766 --> 23:58.141
MAN, THAT KID IS GONNA GET
LAID BY THE TIME HE'S 11.

24:08.028 --> 24:10.533
SWEET DREAMS.

24:10.567 --> 24:13.171
